Package: parappend
Type: Package
Title: Parallel-Safe File Appending with File Locks
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Ao","Lan",role=c("aut", "cre"),email="lanao15@126.com"))
Description: Provides parallel-safe functions to append data to files 
    using OS-level file locks. Supports parallel::mclapply, parLapply,
    and other multi-process workflows. Ensures data integrity during concurrent writing.
URL: https://github.com/now2014/parappend
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports: data.table, filelock
Depends: R (>= 3.1.1)
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
NeedsCompilation: no
